You are here:
Opportunities with Products Report

View information about the products associated with your opportunities, including product name and opportunity stage.

Format: Matrix
Summary Fields: Total Price (sum)
Selected Columns:
  Opportunity Information:
    Opportunity Name
    Amount
    Close Date
    Stage
    Age
    Type
    Probability
    Created Date
  Product Information:
    Product Name
    Product Code
    Quantity
    Active Product
    Sales Price
    Product Date
    Product Description
    Total Price
    Product: Month
    List Price
  Opportunity Owner Information:
    Opportunity Owner
    Owner Role
  Account: General Information:
    Account Name
title: Salesforce Opportunity Product Report
